Introduction

Bel is a South Korean rapper and singer. He was also a member of DUSTIN and its sub unit DUSTIN-ON under Na Entertainment. He left the group when they disbanded on May 24, 2021 and he wasn't apart of the lineup when the group reformed.

In 2023, he participated in MBN' survival show "Show King Night" as part of the group URSA MAJOR.
